reviews.review_text: Thx for sharing your First Master! I remember my first master made on a my new D5 purchased the day before in Manhattan on the way to the Summer Solstice show in Albany, 6-21-95.  I was a 1st Gen trooper forever before that show. Schoeps FOB 15th row stealth maniacs my bros were, or Schoeps front row center pit... man it is hard to be a taper when you are dancing all over the place! Only 9 shows recorded on that Sony.  Summertimes done come and gone, my, oh, my.
